noexcept function\" to be reference compatible with a type \"noexcept function\"?", "CreationDate": "2016-01-06T18:31:56.027", "Id": "34640215", "CommentCount": "4", "LastEditDate": "2016-01-06T19:59:54.910", "PostTypeId": "1", "LastEditorUserId": "2756719", "LastActivityDate": "2016-01-06T19:59:54.910", "Tags": "<c++><reference><language-lawyer><c++1z>", "Score": "3", "OwnerUserId": "1042389", "ClosedDate": "2016-01-22T05:55:29.647", "AnswerCount": "0"}});